<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Refund processed</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background-color: #1a5c3b; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .header p { color: #a0d4b8; margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .body { padding: 32px 40px; }
    .body p { color: #444444; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px; }
    .order-id { font-family: monospace; background: #f4f4f4; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13px; color: #333; }
    .amount { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a5c3b; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Refund processed</h1>
      <p>Your refund is on its way.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>
        A refund of <strong>{{amount}}</strong> for order <span class="order-id">{{orderId}}</span>
        has been successfully processed.
      </p>
      <div class="amount">{{amount}}</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#888888;text-align:center;">
        Refunds typically appear on your statement within 5–10 business days depending on your bank.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      You received this email because a refund was issued for your account. If this wasn't you, please contact support.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
